org.overture.interpreter.debug

Class DBGPReaderV2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.overture.interpreter.debug.DBGPReader
      • org.overture.interpreter.debug.DBGPReaderV2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class DBGPReaderV2
extends DBGPReader
implements Serializable
    Extended DBGPReader adding support for:
    • In-depth variable inspection.
    • Overture command for writing covtbl files after execution.
    • Overture response. Used to check status after issuing an xcmd Overture
    Author:
    kela
    See Also:
